**Expected Behavior**:
No diagnostic on Populate.

**Actual Behavior**:
IDE0251 is raised on Populate to mark it as readonly. But you can't mark it as readonly; if you do, that then triggers an error on the casting of _values: "error CS9164: Cannot convert expression to 'Span<int>' because it is not an assignable variable"

